104f06a5-ba7c-45f9-a079-6bf08c6cd264.do_description: To make the output, you have to...use green lines to connect blue dots that are in the same line
104f06a5-ba7c-45f9-a079-6bf08c6cd264.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the old one

bf254aa0-60b7-4ac0-8f6d-68cfed14ed62.see_description: In the input, you should see...light blue blocks in different patterns

c2c94f5b-b74c-49d5-ba3c-a11d4d4d6248.do_description: To make the output, you have to...use green lines to connect blue dots that are in the same horizontal or vertical point on the grid
c2c94f5b-b74c-49d5-ba3c-a11d4d4d6248.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same as the old one
c2c94f5b-b74c-49d5-ba3c-a11d4d4d6248.see_description: In the input, you should see...light blue dots
